('', '', 0, 0, 0, 'Lai da las quatter forestas', 'Lai dals quatter chantuns, Lai da las quatter forestas', 'num masculin', 'noun', 'Lake Lucerne, Lake of the Four Forest Cantons', 'Lake Lucerne, Lake of the Four Forest Cantons', 'Lag dils quater Cantuns', 'Lag dils quater Cantuns', 'Lai digls quater cantùns', 'Lai digls quater cantùns', 'Lai dallas Quatter Forestas', 'Lai dallas Quatter Forestas', 'Lej da las quatter Forestas', 'Lej da las quatter Forestas', 'Lai da las quatter Forestas', 'Lai da las quatter Forestas', 'Swiss geography:\nOne of the biggest lakes in Switzerland. In English the term \"Lake Lucerne\" is usually applied to the whole lake, although it is strictly speaking only one arm of it. The full term, rarely used in English, is \"Lake of the Four Forest Cantons\".', 'Lai dals quatter chantuns:\nIl \"Lai dals quatter chantuns\" vegn normalmain translatà simplamain sco \"Lake Lucerne\" en englais.\nFar attent ch\'il n\'ha nagin \"of\" en \"Lake Lucerne\"! \"Lake of the Four Forest Cantons\" dian be spezialists.', '', '', '', 3450),
