('', '', 1, 0, 0, 'Viafier Retica', 'Viafier Retica', 'num feminin', 'noun', 'Rhaetian Railway, Rhätische Bahn, RhB', 'Rhaetian Railway, Rhätische Bahn, RhB', 'Viafier Retica', 'Viafier retica', 'Veiafier retica', 'Veiafier retica', 'Veidafier retica', 'veidafier retica', 'Viafier retica', 'Viafier retica', 'Viafier retica', 'Viafier retica', 'The Rhaetian Railway\'s splendid metre-gauge network serves all the major valleys of Canton Graubünden and connects with bus services to nearly all the Canton\'s villages. The railway includes many marvellous works of engineering and offers numerous spectacular views. A must for any visitor to Graubünden!\nMost visitors arrive from the north using the standard-gauge federal railway and need to change in Landquart or Chur.', '', '', '', '', 7422),
